metadata.name: Hollywood Mia
metadata.description:
Classic Hollywood look. Sunny, high contrast, colorful.

I've somehow for nearly as long as I can remember had this connection to Los Angeles. Not sure where it came from, but the sun, the light, the dreams. There is this feeling that I never could verbalise very well, especially with english not being my first language, but I think these photos I made with the wonderful Mia back in 2019. What a powerful personality in this for me important place.

Funny how my LA friends don't really care about West Hollywood, but to me it feels weirdly enough like a bit of home away from home.
